import React from "react";
import {
  MDBJumbotron,
  MDBContainer,
  MDBRow,
  MDBCol,
  MDBBtn,
  MDBCardBody,
  MDBCardText
} from "mdbreact";

const AboutUsPage = () => {
  return (
    <MDBContainer className="mt-5 text-center">
      <MDBRow>
        <MDBCol md="4">
          <MDBRow>
            <MDBBtn color="blue">Who we are</MDBBtn>
          </MDBRow>
          <MDBRow>
            <MDBBtn color="blue">What we do</MDBBtn>
          </MDBRow>
          <MDBRow>
            <MDBBtn color="blue">Contact us</MDBBtn>
          </MDBRow>
        </MDBCol>
        <MDBCol>
          <MDBJumbotron fluid>
            <MDBContainer>
              <MDBCardBody>
                <MDBCardText>
                  Looking for an Agile Maturity Assessment for your
                  organization? Our experts at Dynamix Agile can deliver an
                  assessment for your organization, regardless of your specific
                  needs.
                </MDBCardText>
                <MDBBtn href="#" color="indigo" class="float-right" rounded>
                  more
                </MDBBtn>
              </MDBCardBody>
            </MDBContainer>
          </MDBJumbotron>
        </MDBCol>
      </MDBRow>
    </MDBContainer>
  );
};

export default AboutUsPage;
